---
AI Assistant uses google/gemini-3-flash-preview for reasoning, with responses rendered via react-markdown.
Full chat history is sent to the edge function for multi-turn context.
History tab has search filtering by contact/summary/transcript and sort by newest/oldest.
Chat auto-scrolls to bottom on new messages.
Local Whisper for transcription, audio archived in private storage with signed URLs.
Responses indicate sources: 📁 (Company Database) or 🌐 (General Knowledge).
